ODPV3.SA.summary: Odontoprev S.A. provides private dental plans. The company operates through Corporate, Small and Medium Sizes, Individual, and Others segments. It manages and sells dental care plans to corporate entities and/or individuals; provides commercial advisory, consulting, and business management services; and develops and licenses software programs. The company also retails and wholesales dental equipment and products, sanitizers, drugs, medicines, pharmaceutical inputs, and related items; provides warehousing, storage, loading, organization, custody of goods, technical, and administrative programming services, as well as general management of goods and business, and services of collecting, sending or delivering mail, documents, and objects or goods. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Barueri, Brazil. Odontoprev S.A. is a subsidiary of Bradesco SaÃºde S.A.

QUAL3.SA.long_name: Qualicorp Consultoria e Corretora de Seguros S.A.
QUAL3.SA.summary: Qualicorp Consultoria e Corretora de Seguros S.A. operates as a healthcare benefits trader, administrator, and health management services provider in Brazil. It provides health plan consultancy, brokerage, heathcare information technology and third party administrator services to government, national and multinational companies. The company also engages in benefits administration, billing, benefits planning consulting, health insurance brokerage, and health risk management services. The company was formerly known as Qualicorp S.A. and changed its name to Qualicorp Consultoria e Corretora de Seguros S.A. in June 2018.
